\begin{abstract}
Working over perfect ground fields of arbitrary characteristic, I
classify minimal normal del Pezzo surfaces containing a 
nonrational singularity.
As an application, I determine the structure of 2-dimensional 
anticanonical models for proper  normal algebraic surfaces.
The anticanonical ring may be non-finitely generated.
However, the anticanonical model is either a proper surface, 
or a proper surface minus a point.
\end{abstract}

